{"tid":687394,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung 量產 10nm SO-DIMM DDR4 記憶體　單條可達 32GB","createTime":"2018-06-02T08:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T14:19:01.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b848e8f329c4ca40e8f8721483eb5c80bbd0d9","tid":687394,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:33:30.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.xfast-hosting.com/2018/05/SAMSUNG-32G-SODIMM111.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.xfast-hosting.com%2F2018%2F05%2FSAMSUNG-32G-SODIMM111.jpg&h=87003aa0&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nSamsung 在官網宣佈量產 10nm 制程記憶體顆粒，這款應用在 SO-DIMM 規格的 DDR4 記憶體，單條最大 32GB，頻率最高可達 2666MHz，同時運行功耗將可以下降39%之多。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.xfastest.com/8030/samsung-10nm-32gb-so-dimm-ddr4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.xfastest.com%2F8030%2Fsamsung-10nm-32gb-so-dimm-ddr4%2F&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=a116bd94\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.xfastest.com/8030/samsung-10nm-32gb-so-dimm-ddr4/</a>"},{"pid":"ab1234259e68131dd405865ec9420920fcdede0d","tid":687394,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:33:55.000Z","msg":"以往在 SO-DIMM 上實現 32GB 記憶體十分困難，例如的 G.SKILL 推出的Ripjaws DDR4-3800 記憶體就是用的 Samsung 高端 B-die 記憶體顆粒，但是需要用到四條 8GB 才能組成 32GB 總容量。今次 Samsung 依靠著顆粒上的優勢，量產出 10nm 級別單顆粒 16Gb（2GB）的記憶體 IC（根據官方資料顯示，這個 10nm 其實是介乎於 10-19nm），最後可以製作出單條 32GB 的 SO-DIMM 記憶體。而且頻率進一步提升至 2666MHz 水平，剛好與現時的高端第八代 Core 處理器相匹配，同時得益於先進納米制程的更低漏電率，其功耗從 7.4W 下降至 4.5W，幅度達到 39% 之多，亦代表有助提升流動平台的續航力。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.xfast-hosting.com/2018/05/Semi_SoDIMM_Infographic_main_1-768x972.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.xfast-hosting.com%2F2018%2F05%2FSemi_SoDIMM_Infographic_main_1-768x972.png&h=d0802020&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"356707191eb154dd9a41a14a9ba6f794cb06b922","tid":687394,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"Samsung 表示推出高容量高規格的 SO-DIMM 記憶體可以説明手提電腦廠商組建性能更強 Gaming Notebook，同時廠商亦會進一步擴展 10nm 制程在存儲領域的應用，未來還會推出 10nm 級別的 LPDDR4、GDDR5、DDR4 記憶體顆粒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.xfast-hosting.com/2018/05/SoDIMM_D-768x432.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.xfast-hosting.com%2F2018%2F05%2FSoDIMM_D-768x432.png&h=08fb3831&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46d280ace2e99ad856b78950fa13eccab8ca43d3","tid":687394,"uid":35660,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:34:42.000Z","msg":"直接用 ssd 當 ram 用啦"},{"pid":"73110bca8d5f3e87e7a2a9339e4e8dd180aa3605","tid":687394,"uid":104658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:35:19.000Z","msg":"幾錢條呀?"},{"pid":"4d97ad77c16b3ce0ed0828aee61abb48ed470f43","tid":687394,"uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"46d280ace2e99ad856b78950fa13eccab8ca43d3","tid":687394,"uid":35660,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:34:42.000Z","msg":"直接用 ssd 當 ram 用啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203af737f970499eeb5b49e2d1aeccfc8da4e4cf","tid":687394,"uid":35660,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4d97ad77c16b3ce0ed0828aee61abb48ed470f43","tid":687394,"uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"46d280ace2e99ad856b78950fa13eccab8ca43d3","tid":687394,"uid":35660,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:34:42.000Z","msg":"直接用 ssd 當 ram 用啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\